Package: scenarioMaker
Type: Package
Title: Build scenarios for the battleVerse
Version: 0.2
Date: 2018-03-19
Authors@R: c(
  person('Benjamin','Ashwell',email='bashwell@ida.org',role=c('cre','aut')),
  person('Kevin','Kirshenbaum',email='kkirshen@ida.org',role=c('aut'))
  )
Description: Thie package lets you build scenarios that are used in the battleVerse series of packages.  These packages are designed to help you analyze sensor system performance.
    scenarioMaker lets you create scenarios, calculate ranges and bearings between targets, and plot the results easily.
